description:
Contents:
 - Town Furs: Mint "Casual clothing for an outing that is made from the fur of beasts."
 - Kid's Town Furs: Mint "Casual kid's clothing for an outing that is made from the fur of beasts."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Clothing Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
 - Fur Beret: Mint "A warm beret made from the fur of beasts."
 *You can buy it at any time in the game shop (Fashion Store in Castle St.) when you purchase it.
name: Town Furs Set(Mint)
